  "Description": {
    "English": "A high-detail radar device, capable of upgrading the scanner technology aboard the Minotaur to Analysis Visor levels.<br><br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> to activate a radar sweep, revealing <span class=\"name name-stellar\">additional points of interest</span> that cannot be located via a Multi-Tool scanner.<br><br>Use the Quick Menu to tune the radar to <span class=\"name name-technology\">specific buildings</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种高细节的雷达设备，可将弥诺陶洛斯上的扫描技术升级到分析面甲级别。<br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>以激活雷达扫描，显示无法通过多用途工具扫描器定位的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">其他重要地点</span>。<br><br>使用快捷菜单微调雷达搜寻<span class=\"name name-technology\">特定建筑</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "精細的雷達裝置，能將彌諾陶洛斯上的掃描器科技升級到分析護目鏡的等級。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 啟動雷達掃測，顯示出工具組掃描器無法找出的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">額外重要地點</span>。<br><br>使用快捷選單調整雷達找出<span class=\"name name-technology\">特定建築</span>。"
  },
